Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.22,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.02,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:59.12,ShowTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.44,Title1,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Tetsuo Wants an Interview
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.56,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.45,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,We have a new teacher joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.45,Office,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Faculty Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:22.60,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,But she doesn't seem to be here \Nyet, so I'll introduce her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:27.37,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She must be awfully impressive \Nto arrive late on her first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.67,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:27.56,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.63,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, that's enough joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:35.15,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, you said you're researching \Ndemi-humans, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:39.00,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of making them the \Ntopic of my college thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.93,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,But dealing with demi-humans\Nis always delicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.45,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,so a simple teacher can't get permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:48.68,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, I've still never \Neven seen a demi-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.89,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the number of demi-humans \Nis really quite low...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.29,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Why choose them as your topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:57.61,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to interview demi-humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.12,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you bring this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.42,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.99,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.84,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.28,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Come up to the front and introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.13,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:15.01,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Um... My train was delayed due \Nto a car inspection, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.37,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,The train I tried to take was very crowded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.89,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, of course. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.52,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind introducing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.43,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.06,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand her being late,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but is a crowded train an excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.61,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose she can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.86,Default,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what I mean is that she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.43,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Satou Sakie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.18,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be teaching math.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.95,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm a demi-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.33,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a succubus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The new teacher's a demi-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.58,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Have you ever met one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.58,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.56,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,In this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.83,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,there are people called "demi-humans" \Nwho possess special qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.84,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Succubi, vampires, dullahans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.36,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,The demi-humans who have been used \Nas motifs in myths and fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.19,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,They have also endured persecution in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:08.10,Welfare,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-human Welfare Division
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.10,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,But discrimination has been less \Ncommon in recent years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:11.60,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,and there's even a welfare \Nsystem for demi-humans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.94,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who live with any sort of disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.94,DemiDivision,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-human Division
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:18.40,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Now, being a demi-human is seen as \Njust another aspect of one's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.45,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Lower it a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you go anywhere for spring break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.28,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.50,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop chatting and start carrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.04,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna keep talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.37,ShowTitle,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H090A08&\fs16}Shizaki High School Opening Ceremony: Order of Service \N\NOpening Address, National Anthem, Approval of New Students, Principal's Address, \NNew Students' Pledge, Current Students' Congratulatory Address, \NReading of Congratulatory Messages, School Song, Closing Address
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.98,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't crooked... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:34.72,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:35.25,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.38,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.01,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takahashi, the biology teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.48,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.09,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.63,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.20,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.18,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet y— Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.94,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.31,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.12,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:56.69,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:01.60,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Um, as I said this morning, I'm a succubus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.96,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's why—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.71,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I dress and act to avoid \Nevoking sexual thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:10.24,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,and refrain from contact with \Nothers as much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.58,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.21,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:16.76,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.34,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed the way you've, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.70,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,been watching me from afar all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.76,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No, that was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:28.16,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,It's troublesome if you approach \Nme purely out of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.48,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.97,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Satou-sensei, you've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.29,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.06,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.08,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,198)}I really blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.82,Time,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1477)}A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.60,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei, about the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.46,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should apologize for my indiscretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.58,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.49,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, so please don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.42,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.52,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,She'll never talk to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.52,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:12.05,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.50,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.06,Default - flashback,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.27,Default - flashback,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.39,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.15,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.36,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.61,Default - flashback,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.93,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a new student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're a teacher here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:33.16,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.34,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing there before \Nthe entrance ceremony, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:40.87,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was trying on my uniform at \Nhome, and I got kind of excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:45.09,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, "All right! I'm gonna \Ngo to school right now!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.89,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,But did you have to run off \Nat top speed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.43,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would run if some weird old guy \Nthey don't know speaks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.97,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Weird old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.81,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,They taught us that in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.56,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.93,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should praise my calm \Ndecision to flee immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.86,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,as well as my swift response to the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:08.03,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.31,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! We don't need to talk about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.96,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.63,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,My classmate isn't feeling well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.83,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Help me carry her to the nurse's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.50,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.72,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-B, Takanashi Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:26.04,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks for coming to \Nlet me know, Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:30.65,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,But I hope there's actually \Nsome way I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.37,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you the health teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.28,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,No, biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.51,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not a teacher for nothing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.98,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I can judge a student's health \Nwith one look at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.56,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,She has no face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.02,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.90,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So she's basically one of \Nthose, right? A dullahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.01,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,A dullahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.83,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,A demi-human whose head is \Nseparate from its body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.06,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I went ahead and carried her \Nhead to the nurse's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.94,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but her body's too heavy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.15,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.40,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,A second demi-human... I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:08.46,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it safe to touch this flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.02,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno... It doesn't look hot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.43,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Stretcher coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.90,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay once I cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.43,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.86,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a snow woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a snow woman, so I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:25.44,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a snow woman, so it's totally okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we've got a snow woman, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.73,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Sensei. Let's get \Nto the nurse's office, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.36,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.88,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three of them, so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.32,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you were the first person I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.91,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.09,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.64,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,You seem pretty calm about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't demi-humans unusual to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.67,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, yeah, I'd say they're unusual,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.71,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but they don't surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.84,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a demi-human, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.51,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.35,Office,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.15,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The snow woman has mild heat \Nexhaustion from P.E. class,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.52,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and the dullahan just has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.85,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:18.20,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking meeting demi-humans \Nis easier than I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.87,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of shocked, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, do you hate demi-humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.06,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.33,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I shouldn't have put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.81,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I actually love demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.42,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:37.46,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I've done all kinds of things to try and \Nmeet them, but nothing worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.39,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about other \Nstuff besides how happy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.26,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:48.45,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you're saying you're \Nhappy you met me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.06,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.90,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Really happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.02,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.84,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hee hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.99,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha ha. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.78,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Well, thanks, Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.08,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:08.16,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you call people like us \N"demi-humans," don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:08.78,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:12.98,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I used the term to go along \Nwith you, but it's outdated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.01,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Outdated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Demi-human" doesn't sound \Ncute at all, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.77,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.46,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it's out of a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.26,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So high school girls like us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.06,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,use "demi" instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.56,Default,Tahahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.52,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Tetsuo wants interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.02,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Demi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.22,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with monster girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Eyecatch,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:42.01,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I asked this morning \Nif you'd forgotten anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.32,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget it, like it's \Nthe obvious thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:49.83,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I know you'll lend me yours, even though \Nyou're mad, which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.52,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.92,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You're always pushing your luck, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.38,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.21,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.95,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my little sister, Himari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.10,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takanashi Himari, from class C.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:06.77,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.01,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.06,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.77,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.43,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,If you doodle in it again, you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:14.44,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.18,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.96,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari and Himari, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.18,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,She seems more responsible \Nthan someone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.20,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's the little sis I'm proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.68,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Is she also a demi-hum—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.20,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,A demi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.30,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.96,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.12,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.49,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.90,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Only if it's okay with you, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to tell you about vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.93,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Of course, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.14,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Only if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.77,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.03,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I thought— You will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:52.91,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.96,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if I talk to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can I come and hang out in \Nthe biology prep room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.90,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure, come by anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.86,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! Okay, I'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.49,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... So, Machi-san, you went to the \Nmiddle school right next to mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:12.10,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to meet someone \Nin this school from so nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.35,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.13,Default,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you also take the bus, Machi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.92,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:21.77,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Isn't that a long walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.32,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,The bus is crowded during school \Ncommuter hours, so it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.91,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, with the way I'm built and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.77,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.64,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! By the way, I found a really \Nfunny video yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.53,Default,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.65,Default,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Machi-san, you watch videos online, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.52,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.30,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look! This cat is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.48,Default,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.54,Default,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.67,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.84,Default,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,That's wild! It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.74,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:58.01,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Demis are more likely to occur as a \Nresult of mutation than genetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:01.46,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,It's entirely possible for only \None twin to be a demi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.65,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,The sisters' relationship aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:07.23,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know anything\Nabout how demis live,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:13.02,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,how they interact with others, how they \Nthink, or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.02,BioRoom,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Biology Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.60,Office,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}how they interact with others, \Nhow they think, or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.15,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,If there's one thing I now know, it's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:21.36,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This room is so nice and dark and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.69,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,...vampires get hot easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.65,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.84,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I did say you could come by anytime, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:31.08,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the sunlight is so\Nbright in my classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:34.00,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd feel bad, making my classmates \Ngo out of their way for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:40.57,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there are lots of things in here \Nthat shouldn't be in direct sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.09,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Sensei, you want to \Ninterview a demi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.01,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I charge a venue fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.35,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.47,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.18,SignB,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Encyclopedia of Vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:52.18,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of the qualities \Nascribed to vampires by legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.13,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:57.27,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I do like garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.27,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Crosses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:02.19,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Crosses are only fashionable \Nthrough middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.45,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Fashionable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.69,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.44,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,A stake through the heart \Nwould kill us! Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.03,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,That would kill me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.60,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Do vampires really have to \Ndrink blood to stay alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.09,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:15.69,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:18.13,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever get anemic, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.60,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Feel short on blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.65,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.63,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sometimes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.34,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we often feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.07,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, we prefer \Nto stay out of the sun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.53,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So if we're careful about what \Nwe eat, we can get by okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.54,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.39,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Liver! I love liver and onions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.84,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And also tomato juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels just like drinking blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.83,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like drinking blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that you really do desire blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:48.15,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah... Maybe I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.30,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires are provided with \Nblood by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We get one pack per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.50,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:59.19,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe drinking that makes it so \NI can get by on the food I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.95,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:06.00,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there are some vampires who get \Nby without relying on that blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.00,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.51,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of those vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.30,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.21,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.97,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:21.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, S-Sensei! Give me one \Nmore chance, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.46,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never ask another favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.06,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There are vegetarians, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.25,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.24,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,They survive without eating meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.64,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.24,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.64,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're pretty amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That! It's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.66,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I really get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.92,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.75,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you ever want \Nto take blood directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.56,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.20,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Stories say people you drink \Nfrom become vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.85,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,or that you can make them your servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.62,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what your fangs are for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.32,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Ever want to use them to suck blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do! I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.30,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:04.98,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Recently... Oh, you know that snow \Nwoman in the class next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.21,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the one from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.53,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's a snow woman, \Nher body feels so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:08.88,Default,HikariBG,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.54,Default,YukiBG,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Whoa! T-Takanashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.15,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.15,Default,HikariBG,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mm, you feel so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.60,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,so I cling to her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.31,Default,HikariBG,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Aw, what's the problem? \NWe both hate heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:18.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when I get a look \Nat the nape of her neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:18.62,Default,YukiBG,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But this feels hot to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:23.92,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I think, "Ah, her body is cold, \Nbut I bet her blood is warm,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:27.46,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and "I bet that contrast would feel \Ngreat if I sucked her blood,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:32.39,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and "I'd love to see how she struggles \Nand the pain showing on her face."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.40,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I do think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.56,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do it, though, since she'd hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:41.43,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... That seems a bit erotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.61,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? It does?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.90,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. Guess you weren't aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.37,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever want to suck the \Nblood of the opposite sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:50.90,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:54.46,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,No? You prefer girls' blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.41,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it isn't that, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:01.83,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's probably because \NI've never been in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:07.39,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, sucking blood is an \Nexpression of sexual desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.05,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,So fantasizing about sucking girls' \Nblood could pass for a joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.28,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,but you still have some reservations \Nabout doing it with boys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.10,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do! You're too quick on the uptake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:20.07,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that I'd know, but it seems \Nlike sadistic behavior, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.78,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And my type is someone who's dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:26.85,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe it would be really hard for \Nme to do that. Or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.26,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.90,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.16,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You were thinking it's nice to be young,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.44,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,or I'm making the most of my youth, \Nor some other old man's thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.41,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,You're quick on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.87,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.50,Default - italics,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,This vampire-chan is at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.17,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,It was insensitive of me to ask all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:48.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who said you could ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.54,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,This has been fun. I've learned \Na lot from you. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.40,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.56,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly. We have classes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.95,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.55,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,See? There's the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to class. Back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.89,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.78,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.96,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So, were you surprised? Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.98,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sink your teeth into me, \Neven by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That was kinda erotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.26,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,World History
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.80,Default,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Machi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.92,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.57,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Macchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.73,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,M-Macchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.90,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you feeling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.23,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.70,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You have it pretty rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:04.78,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you have to carry your head \Neverywhere you go, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:06.79,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Going to and from school must be even worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:14.53,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Carrying your bag would take one \Nhand, so that'd be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.74,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:19.80,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Not really... I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.51,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.13,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it inconvenient, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:24.96,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.44,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm a vampire, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.98,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So I totally get what you're going through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.19,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.69,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in my case, I can't\Nstand strong sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.17,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.70,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,In summer, I can't even wear short sleeves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But vampires can't stand to be hot, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.64,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.70,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to cover my body \Nin cold compresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.87,Default,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.70,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The injustices of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:54.91,Default,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.03,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,So, Takanashi-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Hikari."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.39,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never see you during breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.67,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.10,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.84,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.48,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,You're Machi Kyouko, from 1-B, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.82,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Er, I guess asking your body's pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.38,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,To Takahashi-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.50,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.75,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.05,Default - italics,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:50.52,Default - italics,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for carrying me to the \Nnurse's office when I had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.32,Default - italics,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-chan told me about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.73,Default - italics,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd be happy to talk to you \Nabout being a demi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.76,Default - italics,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to thank you \Npersonally for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.03,Default - italics,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,May I come and talk to you sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.03,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to thank you personally for your help. \NMay I come and talk to you sometime? \N1-B Machi Kyouko
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:03.99,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.95,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't hear his answer \Nwith only your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.53,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.71,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote my answer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.10,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Carry it back, and don't drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.64,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-chan, I did it! I got his answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:26.93,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.19,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.98,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.86,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that was nerve-wracking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.05,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.48,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.15,Office,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}Machi, \NFeel free to come by anytime. \NTakahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.32,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:46.82,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.59,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.57,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:53.12,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop somewhere on the way \Nhome. We can get drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.22,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. That sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:58.23,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Where should we go? \NWhat should we drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:00.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like, Macchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.30,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
